<div class="global-container">
<div class="container2 justify-content-center">
  <h2 class="text-center mb-0">My Profile</h2>
</div>


<div class="container2" data-controller="edit-profile">
  <div class="user-info my-3">
    <div data-edit-profile-target="infos">
      <h2 class="mb-4">My Metrics <i class="fa-solid fa-pen-to-square" data-action="click->edit-profile#displayForm"></i></h2>
        <p>PROFILE PICTURE HERE</p>
        <p><strong>Name: </strong> <%= current_user.username %></p>
        <p><strong>Email: </strong><%= current_user.email %></p>
        <p><strong>Age: </strong><%= current_user.age %></p>
        <p><strong>Weight: </strong><%= current_user.weight %></p>
        <p><strong>Height: </strong><%= current_user.height %></p>
        <p><strong>Gender: </strong><%= current_user.gender %></p>
    </div>
      <!-- Simple form to edit user information -->
      <%= simple_form_for current_user, html: {class: "d-none"}, data: { edit_profile_target: "form" } do |f| %>
        <%= f.input :username, label: false, input_html: { class: 'profile-input' } %>
        <%= f.input :email, label: false, input_html: { class: 'profile-input' } %>
        <%= f.input :age, label: false, input_html: { class: 'profile-input' } %>
        <%= f.input :weight, label: false, input_html: { class: 'profile-input' } %>
        <%= f.input :height, label: false, input_html: { class: 'profile-input' } %>
        <%= f.input :gender, label: false, input_html: { class: 'profile-input' } %>
        <%= f.button :submit, class: "workoutbtn mb-3" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
</div>
 <div class="container2 user-goal">
    <h2>My Goals <i class="fa-solid fa-pen-to-square"></i></h2>
      <p>Weight Loss</p>
      <p>For those aiming to achieve their weight loss goals through our gym app, it's essential to design a workout routine that focuses on calorie burn, muscle toning, and overall fitness. To start, prioritize cardio exercises like running, cycling, or jumping rope, as they are excellent for torching calories and improving cardiovascular health. These activities help create a calorie deficit, which is crucial for shedding pounds.</p>
      <p>You have a total of X cardio exercises planned this month. Go and create a workout now!</p>
      <%= link_to "Home", root_path, class:"button-green mb-3" %>
    </div>

